title: There is no elo hell. But...
body:
I was given the privilege of playing with Mr. No English {{champion:64}}   tonight. He's 0/8 for the season so far. His no english duo partner didn't have a record too much better (5W10L).

But in all seriousness, how did the system decide to place someone with a 100% loss rate with ~S3? S3 was higher than his last season's max bracket.

I'm not amazing. I have a long way to go. There is no elo hell, but this is why it's a rough climb.

QQ Salty asf.

Our Jax was also 2W18L from his last 20. pls riet. pls
